'Obviously fake, but still absolutely hilarious!' wrote YouTube user Chubzdoomer.

YouTube user Kenrick Eason agreed:

'Even though this is fake it was the reaction of millions!!! Even Patriot fans was like WTF!! Who call pass at the goal line on 2nd down with one time out left!!' he said. 

